  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>This game is best enjoyed with a group of friends! </strong><br>Chaotic Conflicts is a casual and chaotic  MULTIPLAYER FPS game. In this chaotic shooter you'll try to shoot your way to the top of the scoreboard while competing with other players in a free for all match.<br><br> Players however aren't the only threat. You'll also have to face off against many random events that happen throughout the match. You can go up against tornadoes, robots, zombies, bombs, and much more! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873380/extras/8a0ab426480d2a3543453d40379e451a.poster.avif?t=1733737033\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873380/extras/8a0ab426480d2a3543453d40379e451a.webm?t=1733737033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873380/extras/8a0ab426480d2a3543453d40379e451a.mp4?t=1733737033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then there is the wave survival mode. A survival game mode inspired by Call of Duty Zombies. In this game mode you'll have to fight off wave after wave of robots. Your only goal is to last as long as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>This game is best enjoyed with a group of friends! </strong><br>Chaotic Conflicts is a casual and chaotic  MULTIPLAYER FPS game. In this chaotic shooter you'll try to shoot your way to the top of the scoreboard while competing with other players in a free for all match.<br><br> Players however aren't the only threat. You'll also have to face off against many random events that happen throughout the match. You can go up against tornadoes, robots, zombies, bombs, and much more! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873380/extras/8a0ab426480d2a3543453d40379e451a.poster.avif?t=1733737033\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873380/extras/8a0ab426480d2a3543453d40379e451a.webm?t=1733737033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2873380/extras/8a0ab426480d2a3543453d40379e451a.mp4?t=1733737033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then there is the wave survival mode. A survival game mode inspired by Call of Duty Zombies. In this game mode you'll have to fight off wave after wave of robots. Your only goal is to last as long as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
